description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Mammographer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Competitive Salary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Springfield Hospital&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Join us on our exciting journey of new developments and expansion over the coming months. Here at Springfield we provide a wide range of services including Surgery, Medicine, Oncology, Plastic and Cosmetic surgery, and Paediatrics. We are continually introducing new technology to ensure we provide the best experience for our patients and support for our hard working teams and have just opened 2 additional purpose built theatres taking our total to 6. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We have opportunities for experienced Mammographers to join the imaging team. The department covers theatres, CT, MRI and Ultrasound. You will be supported by one of the UK’s largest private health care groups who will ensure your continuous development and sponsor additional post-graduate and other learning courses.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you are looking for your next move and want to join a friendly team with a real sense of community within the working environment, then look no further!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;What we can offer you:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Competitive salary&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;25 days annual leave plus the option to buy more&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contributory Pension Scheme&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Access to the Ramsay Academy – genuine opportunities to grow, develop and specialise in your career&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Private Healthcare&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Life Assurance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Free parking and subsidised staff restaurant&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;HCPC registered a member of the Society of Radiographers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mammography Certified with XRay experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sound written and verbal communication skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proven ability to work effectively in a team environment and independently as required&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Passion to deliver high quality diagnostic services&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ramsay Healthcare UK is a high quality provider of acute private healthcare across the UK. We have a highly specialised team of dedicated staff who work within this multi- speciality setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Springfield Hospital opened in 1987 and is one of Essex’s leading private hospitals. It is a 64 bedded hospital all with ensuite facilities, with parent and child rooms, a 14 bed Day unit and a high dependency unit. There are six operating theatres, a physiotherapy department and on site private GP service. The Hospital has a full range of diagnostic equipment including CT, MRI, X-ray and ultrasound.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
